<p><a title="Butterscotch Candy on Foodista" href="http://www.foodista.com/recipe/MD53DBT7/butterscotch-candy"><img alt="Butterscotch Candy on Foodista" src="http://dyn.foodista.com/content/embed/b2_MD53DBT7_94e85223b32d98a4ddea76a05df6a94869d218a4.png?foodista_widget_G8FQYL6D" style="border:none;width:300px;height:175px;" /></a></p></div>
